1. *Događaj* je planiran za sutra. (The *event* is scheduled for tomorrow.)
2. On je bio prisutan na tom *događaju*. (He was present at that *event*.)
3. Taj *događaj* će se pamtiti još dugo. (That *event* will be remembered for a long time.)
4. Izveštaj o *događaju* je veoma detaljan. (The report about the *event* is very detailed.)
5. *Događaji* su se brzo odvijali. (The *events* were unfolding quickly.)
6. Organizatori *događaja* su bili veoma zadovoljni. (The organizers of the *event* were very satisfied.)
7. Na *događaju* je bilo mnogo zvanica. (There were a lot of guests at the *event*.)
8. *Događaj* je izazvao veliku pažnju medija. (The *event* attracted a lot of media attention.)
9. Tokom *događaja* smo imali priliku da upoznamo mnogo zanimljivih ljudi. (During the *event*, we had the opportunity to meet many interesting people.)
10. Mnogi su se nadali da će taj *događaj* biti veliki uspeh. (Many were hoping that the *event* would be a great success.)